<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head.ejs') %>
  <title>2k17 — Class Social Space</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <nav class="large-and-medium">
      <h1>2k17 ❤️</h1>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Donate</a></li>
        <li><a href="/members">Members</a></li>
        <li><a href="/login" class="login-btn">Login</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <nav class="small-only">
      <span class="menu-icon fas fa-bars-sort" onclick="toggleMenu()"></span>
      <p class="brand">2k17 ❤️</p>
      <button class="login-btn" onclick="window.location.href = '/login'">Login</button>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h2>Welcome to <span style="color: blue;">2</span><span style="color: green;">k</span><span style="color: red;">1</span><span style="color: yellow;">7</span></h2>
        <p>Private space to reconnect, share moments, and relive memories for the 2017-24 batch of JNV Chandrapur</p><br>
        <a href="/create-account" class="cta-btn">Get Started &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class="fal fa-arrow-right"></span></a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="about-and-newsletter">
    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
      <h3>What is 2k17?</h3>
      <p>This isn’t just another social media site — it’s a digital time capsule. 2k17 exists for the quiet moments — when you’re feeling a little nostalgic, when you want to see a familiar face or check where someone is, or when a memory from school suddenly resurfaces. It’s not about daily posts or endless scrolling. It’s about checking in once in a while, smiling at something someone shared, and remembering the chaos, laughter, and friendships that shaped those seven years. This place will be here — quietly, patiently — whenever you feel like coming home for a bit.
</p>
    </section>

    <section id="newsletter-sub" class="newsletter-sub">
      <h3>Subscribe to our Newsletter</h3>
      <p>Stay updated with the latest news and updates from 2k17 with a monthly email.</p>
      <form action="/subscribe" method="POST">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
      <br><br>
    </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section id="features" class="features no-select">
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="fal feature-icon fa-shield-keyhole"></span>
          <h4>Private & Secure</h4>
          <p>Access limited to classmates only — no outsiders allowed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="fal feature-icon fa-layer-group"></span>
          <h4>Share Posts</h4>
          <p>Post text and pictures to remember our best moments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="fal feature-icon fa-square-heart"></span>
          <h4>Comment & Like</h4>
          <p>Engage with your batchmates' posts like never before.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <span class="fal feature-icon fa-images"></span>
          <h4>Class Memories</h4>
          <p>A living scrapbook — from class 6 to whole life</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

